tinued Claim Form and every two weeks, you must  	turn it in.<br> 	<b>A:</b> When I fill out the Continued Claim Form, what will I need to tell them?<br> 	<b>B:</b> You must show where and when you tried to look for work. If you earned  	any money, you need to tell them about it.<br> 	<b>A:</b> What other information does the form ask for?<br> 	<b>B:</b> You have to tell them if you were too sick to work on any of the days  	that you should have been looking for work.<br>
